Saw @dorisgoz and @7elevensg cooking challenge👩🏻‍🍳✨ and decided to join the fun cos why not😂 been wanting to try the chicken Briyani after seeing @foodkingnoc and @thejianhaotan 7 eleven video😊 i twerk it into a chicken briyani baked rice🍛 where you just need a oven/microwave and cheese 🧀 ! Fast 10-15 mins work and you get a zing up cheese pull chicken Briyani at home🔥 and I got to say it is as good as the reviews👍
